FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:resolve

COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

LABEL maintainer="analytics-team" \
      version="1.0" \
      description="Java analytics dashboard with cloud database support"

WORKDIR /app

RUN apk add --no-cache \
    curl \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates && \
    mkdir -p /tmp/certs && \
    cd /tmp/certs && \
    wget -q https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem && \
    wget -q https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca -file global-bundle.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt || true && \
    keytool -import -alias digicert-ca -file DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt || true && \
    rm -rf /tmp/certs && \
    apk del ca-certificates

RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app

COPY --from=builder /build/target/*.jar /app/app.jar
RUN chown -R app:app /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
